activities:
Publicis Groupe affiliates in the United States will use and otherwise process European Employee Data in the United States for human resources and compliance purposes, including:
•	compensation administration and financial planning; 
•	monitoring and enforcing compliance with company policies and procedures, including adoption of disciplinary measures; 
•	organizational and workforce administration and planning; 
•	training and employee development; 
•	career development, training, talent management and succession planning; 
•	providing IT support and services; 
•	creating and managing employee directories; 
•	mailing and e-mailing lists; 
•	complying with law enforcement and government authority requests; 
•	and addressing litigation and related issues.
